</ul>

<h3 id="储存区域网络storage-attachment-networksan"><a href="http://baike.baidu.com/view/120921.htm#sub6204565">储存区域网络(Storage Attachment Network,SAN)</a></h3>

<p>SAN是将许多存储装置</p>

